{"content": "<h2>Mint Your 1st Artwork on BTC Workshop</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>​<strong>In this course, you will inscribe your art on Bitcoin</strong>​<strong>…with digital provenance that unlocks art collectors on BTC.</strong></p><p>​🗓️Fri 28th Feb 930am NZT (60 mins) <a href=\"https://everytimezone.com\">convert timezone</a><br />​🗓️Sun 1st Mar 930am NZT (60 mins)<a href=\"https://everytimezone.com\">convert timezone</a> <br />​🗓️Tue 3rd Mar 930am NZT (60 mins) <a href=\"https://everytimezone.com\">convert timezone</a></p><p>​👨‍🏫 5 Course Modules ​<br />1. Create Artist Ordinals Vault ​<br />2. Connect Vault To Inscribing Wallet <br />3. ​Fund Inscribing Wallet with BTC <br />4. ​Inscribe Artist Token ​<br />5. Inscribe Your Collection on BTC<br /><br /><em>Sessions are not recorded so please ensure you can attend.</em></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Request to Join Workshop</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Artists must be on The Line to be approved for the workshop. You may attend camera on or off. We recommend camera on for the group work.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<iframe\n  src=\"https://lu.ma/embed/event/evt-05SkFVGJys7JyEK/simple\"\n  width=\"600\"\n  height=\"700\"\n  frameborder=\"0\"\n  style=\"border: 1px solid #bfcbda88; border-radius: 4px;\"\n  allowfullscreen=\"\"\n  aria-hidden=\"false\"\n  tabindex=\"0\"\n></iframe>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>The Promise</h2>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"403\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-1024x551.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-1024x551.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-300x162.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-768x414.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-1536x827.png 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-2048x1103.png 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-1320x711.png 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.36.08 PM-600x323.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>The Format</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Workshops are highly interactive and fast paced with your host MintFace. Be prepared to work together in groups and participate in live q&amp;a's. This ain't no boomer slideshow!</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"418\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-1024x572.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-1024x572.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-300x168.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-768x429.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-1536x859.png 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-2048x1145.png 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-1320x738.png 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.44.04 PM-600x335.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Get Your BTC Wallets Setup</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>For artists confident on Ethereum, you'll get a vault and inscribing wallet setup during the workshop.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-1024x539.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-1024x539.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-300x158.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-768x404.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-1536x808.png 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-2048x1078.png 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-1320x694.png 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.38.46 PM-600x316.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Get Wallets Funded</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Get your BTC wallets funded ready for inscription. You'll need to budget around $200USD per inscription as the art is stored on-chain...so is spendy.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"415\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-1024x568.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-1024x568.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-300x166.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-768x426.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-1536x852.png 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-2048x1136.png 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-1320x732.png 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.39.15 PM-600x333.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Get Your Collection Inscribed</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>There are many ways to get your collection inscribed on BTC. We explore the pros and cons of each and support you through the process in between the live sessions.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"411\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-1024x562.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-1024x562.png 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-300x165.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-768x421.png 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-1536x843.png 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-1320x724.png 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM-600x329.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-14-at-4.50.14 PM.png 1994w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<iframe\n  src=\"https://lu.ma/embed/event/evt-05SkFVGJys7JyEK/simple\"\n  width=\"600\"\n  height=\"700\"\n  frameborder=\"0\"\n  style=\"border: 1px solid #bfcbda88; border-radius: 4px;\"\n  allowfullscreen=\"\"\n  aria-hidden=\"false\"\n  tabindex=\"0\"\n></iframe>"}